tlon of tho candidates by\ntho leaders, or what Is no better, by\na few metropolitan papers, Is not\nonly undemocratic but nbsurd. The\nrank and fllo of tho Democratic party\nare In no mood to havo cither Mr.\nJrnn or any ono olso tell them what\nthey ought to do.\nBryan has either tho power to co\nerce tho voters Into tho selection of\nnny particular candldato nor hns he\ndisposition t0 exercise such power\ncen If such a powor were his.\"\nAppefte--None.\nThe Woeful Reflections of Withered\nDyspeptic.\nNo substltuto for good nature has\nyet been found. Smiles tako root In\ntho stomach. Without good digestion\nthere never can bo any Bunshlno, for\ntho very simple reason that the stom\nach and tho brain aro twins, and what\nuffocts ono Invariably affocts tho\nother. Tho ad a go that tho best road\nto a porson's hoart is via tho stom\nach, still holds good.\nGorged grub and pappy plo always\nbreed gloom and sleepless nights.\nThoy also brood dyspepsia quick\ndyspopsla, and dyspepsia shows Itsolf\nIn a variety vf ways belching, bum-\n1 aArt i ji (Mlm\n1 twl yiMlm\nmm am\n3\nc\nArrives in Washington\nWith Oheerful View of\nFinancial Situation\nfor\nThroughout the State Preparing\nCampaign Against Present\nCounty Salary Law.\nEvidences nro plenty In ovory other\ncounty In tho stato as woll as In\nBt ark, that county officials nro not\nsatisfied with tho existing county sal\nary law and will make a strenuous\nrfort to havo It repealed or anion 1\ncd at the coming bcsslon of tho legis\nlature This wook tho county dorks\nof tho stato held a secret session at\nfiprlngflold and thoro dotormtned, so\ntr as could bo learned to tako some\naction which would tend to bring tho\nHatter forcibly to tho attontlon of tho\nliwraakers of tho stato.\nTho samo rumor comos from Co\nlumbus whoro it Is said tho various\nassociations of county officers will\nmako a united effort In this direction.\nIt Is said, In connection with this, that\nwhen tho officials of tbo larger coun\nties saw that