ing Party.\nA Jolly orowd of 18 couples charter\ned a special car and held a dance rl\nSponselier's tail, New Berlin, last\noil hi, A delightful luuoh was served,\ntfhe party returned to C&nton at I; 30\nftttr having a pleasant tlmey\nIs This You?\nIng sensation, an ompty feeling In\ntht Ptomach, bloating after eating,\nbrash, aversion to food, formentatlou\nor downright Indigestion.\nThoro nro fow diseases which create\nsuch misery, long drawn out misery,\nas dyspepsia. It pursues you ue\nforo meals;-you take It to bed with\nyou; It Is with you at tho thcatro and\nat your desk.\nWhnt Is tho only way to get rid of\nItT\nYou don't havo to stop eating, you\ndon't hnvo to diet. Just tako somo\nthing that will do tho work of tho\nstomach and let tho stomach take n\nrest.\nStuart's Dyspopsla Tablets aro th\nmost wonderful llttlo tablots on earth\nfor this very thing.\nIn plain arithmetic, 1 of Stuart'\"\nDjspcpsla Tablots equals 1 good strong\nstomach for 1 time for 1 good hcartv\nmoal. Ono Ingredient of Stuart'\nDyspepsia Tablots will digest Pr\nfectly 3,000 grains of food In Just th\nsamo way that a strong, robust\nhealthy stomach would do It,\nStuart's Dyspepsia Tablets enrich\nand incrcaso the gastric Juice In your\nstomach, and that Is mostly what you\nneed, moro and bottor gastrlo Julco\nAnd It gives tho stomach a-rest, a good\nlong rest. In tho meantlmo it euros\nthe dyspopsla, and all othor stomach\ntroubles,\nJust a few of Stuart's Dyspepsia\nTablets will provo to you what thoso\nllttlo cherubs of health and happlnojs\ncan do.\nStuart's Dyspepsia Tablots nro fo.\nsalo at all drug storos for COc a box.\nSend us your name and address to\nday and wo will at once sond you by\nmall a samplo packago froo. Addrojv\ni A. Stuart Co., ISO Stuart Bldg..\nMarshall, Mich.\nAlliance Since the arrost of \"Dr.\"\nAdams at WellsvJUo of the Boy Pho\nnomonon retinue, eoveral porsons who\nwere faked hero havo Inquired how\nthoy can get their monoy, illegally paid\nto \"Dr.\" Adams,